title: Little Zoo
description:
Little Zoo is the trusted home of fun animated content, which comes with a guarantee of positive values for your child.  

It's a brand new YouTube channel for kids packed with delightful stories and characters, delivered in the most engaging ways.

Get ready for number fun with the Numberblocks, word magic adventures with the Alphablocks, creative escapades with Olive the Ostrich, enlightening adventures with Millie and Lou and the Forest Folkies - and brand new shows coming soon! 

Little Zoo is brought to you by the Multi BAFTA award-winning animation studio, Blue Zoo, and Alphablocks Ltd.

Subscribe and tune in to Little Zoo for new episodes and compilations every week!

For more Millie and Lou fun visit https://www.millieandlou.com

title: Alphablocks
description:
The Alphablocks are 26 living letters who discover that whenever they hold hands and make a word, something magical happens. With adventures, songs and silliness, it’s tons of fun with words – all built on a firm foundation of key phonics skills.

Alphablocks is the hit CBeebies TV show that’s already helped hundreds of thousands of children to learn to read, and will bring phonics to life for anyone wishing to learn how to spell in English.  For additional teaching notes, please click in the description.

title: Colourblocks
description:
Colourblocks helps children to see and understand colours in a new way. Each episode is carefully crafted with the help of leading global colour experts, child experts and brought to life by BAFTA award-winning animation studio, Blue Zoo Productions.

It's the story of a group of friends, who use Colour Magic to bring Colourland to life in the most vibrant way!

title: Learning Blocks
description:
The Alphablocks are 26 living letters who discover that whenever they hold hands and make a word, something magical happens. With adventures, songs and silliness, it’s tons of fun with words – all built on a firm foundation of key phonics skills. Alphablocks is the hit CBeebies TV show that’s already helped hundreds of thousands of children to learn to read, and will bring phonics to life for anyone wishing to learn how to spell in English.  

The Numberblocks are little blocks with big ideas, having a ton of number fun! Learn how to add, subtract and count in a fun and educational way using singular blocks to do basic maths sums.They play games and sing songs about how easy it is to count! Numberblocks is a hit CBeebies show that is teaching children around the world how to count with easy to more advanced levels of numeracy for children.

title: CBeebies
description:
This CBeebies YouTube channel is aimed at adults watching with children and offers a safe environment where CBeebies content is readily accessible with no inappropriate links or adverts.  

CBeebies is dedicated to delighting and surprising its pre-school audience and it remains the UK's most watched and most loved channel for the under-sixes. For even more fun games and videos for your pre-schooler in a safe child friendly environment, visit us at http://www.bbc.co.uk/cbeebies

title: Mojo Swoptops
description:
The little truck that SWOPS its TOP!

Mojo is a vehicle with a difference – it can be anything and everything at the swop of a top!  With a fresh and imaginative approach to problem solving, Mojo swops predictable outcomes for exciting adventures – learning and laughing along the way. Together with best friend Bo, Mojo brings curiosity and a mischievous sense of fun to every challenge.

Mojo and Bo love to help their local community of Swoppiton and when the call comes in, it’s time to SWOP that TOP!  With a wide choice of tops at their disposal at their Swopshop HQ, Mojo can become whatever vehicle is best suited to the task.  Be it fire truck, helicopter, bulldozer, our heroes are sure to get the job done, though seldom in the way they first imagine!

Join Mojo and Bo in exciting adventures in this brand new cartoon for kids!

title: Alphablocks Français
description: Les Alphablocks sont 26 lettres animées qui découvrent que lorsqu'elles se tiennent la main et forment un mot, quelque chose de magique se produit. Entre chanson et fantaisie, cette aventure fondée sur la phonétique fait le plein de mots dans la joie et la bonne humeur. La série télé à succès de CBeebies, qui a déjà aidé des centaines de milliers d'enfants à apprendre à lire, est de retour avec une version française conçue pour enseigner l'anglais en tant que deuxième langue. Les petits apprendront à lire, écrire et épeler l'anglais en acquérant toutes sortes de compétences : l'alphabet anglais, l'assemblage de lettres, les familles de mots et bien plus encore.
